column5: happy birthday cliff
Happy bday Big Cliff!  Have a great one!

Happy Birthday, Cliff!!  What were you doing working today?  I think I saw you at Burnham Gardens today, though I didn't know it until you left.  Strange combination you're selling, the coffee I understand, but washroom supplies? You're not trying to cut my grass are you.
Happy Birthday

Thank you all so much for the kind words, PMs, and text messages! Princess, thank you so much for the beautiful poem, I really enjoyed it!  I have been looking forward to this day for a long time, I feel like I am entering my second child hood, don't need a fishing license, the government sends me money every month just for being here, Sue keeps telling me to grow up and that I already have enough toys LOL.  Anyway, thanks again one and all, it really made my day!
The next step back  in your 2nd childhood puts you in diapers ya know...   Art
Happy Birthday Cliff Hope you had a great day    and wish all the best Leechman
Happy Birthday Cliff
Happy birthday Cliff.  A
Happy Birthday !!
Happy Birthday Cliff
Happy Birthday Cliff!
Happy Birthday Cliff!! Hope you had a great day.
Happy B-day Cliff.....Many many more to ya...TC....Chuck...

Just want to send a special Happy Birthday wish to you Dad. I found this poem that made me think of you. Hope you have a wonderful day. Love you Teressa  My Fishing Hole  I'm going down to my fishing hole, Got my tackle box, and fishing pole. Gonna catch a mess of fish for lunch, Fry em up in my pan, I love that crunch.  With a bitsy minnow on my line, I'll catch enough, so all can dine. Hoping for blue gills and sunfish too, I love fishing that's what I do.  I got a sandwich and a couple of beers, I do love fishing, I hold it dear. Look at this fishing hole, what a beautiful sight, Hold on, hold on now, I got a bite.  by Juan Olivarez
Happy Birthday Cliff - hope you have a GREAT day!    Tracker (Don)
Happy B-DAY fella. Have a great day Cliff.
Happy B-Day Cliff, all the best to ya !!
Happy birthday Cliff! Take the day off.
Happy Birthday Cliff, have a good one...
Enjoy your day Cliff!
A "BIG" Happy Birthday to you Cliff, I hope it's most enjoyable.
Happy Birthday
A very happy birthday Cliff..
Happy Bday Cliff!!!
Have a super Day Cliff, Happy Birthday  Joey
Yet another chapter completed in the book of your life...may it be a never ending story ..  Happy Birthday
Happy Birthday Cliff, I'll toast you a STEAM  later today. Cheers!!  All the best, Simon
Want a Kleenex Dad, Happy Birthday Cliff Birthdays don't get any better than that.
Happy Birthday Cliff, have a good one!
Happy Birthday, Cliff!!
Hope you have a fantastic day Cliff!!!  Happy Birthday!  And Teressa...a wonderful poem and post to your dad!
Happy Birthday Big Cliff!!!!!!!!!! Are you officially 40 now or is this 39?  Enjoy the day Cliff, you earned it. Teressa, great peom.  From The Wight House
Have a great one Cliff.   Glad to have met you this past June.
WOW !!!...No more fishing licenses and the federalies send you a cheque every month just for being old...LOL  Have a good one my friend...
Happy Birthday Cliff, You have been such a good person so this year does not count against you.  Art
Congrats on making it back to free fishing Cliff !!
Free Fishing, I guess you have to have at least one good benefit for reaching that milestone. Happy BDay Cliff, all the best to you!!!
Yep free fishing  :thumbsup_anim:   Gotta love that. Happy B-day buddy...and many more to follow.
